data.title: May 2023 Metropolitan and Nonmetropolitan Area Occupational Employment and Wage Estimates
data.text:
Each area name is a link to its occupational employment and wage estimates. Choose an area below, or view metropolitan and nonmetropolitan area estimates listed by county or town.

Metropolitan and nonmetropolitan areas are listed below by State. In the case of cross-State metropolitan areas, metropolitan areas with boundaries that cross State borders, the metropolitan area name appears under every State which contains part of that metropolitan area. For metropolitan and nonmetropolitan area definitions used by the OEWS survey, see the MSA definitions page.
